name: Street Race - The Business End
creator: RSI_sidhant
desc: Pay cuts, lack of safety equipment, Taco Bomb Tuesdays abolished, and now street racers juiced on cans of Junk are cutting through the construction site. These contractors are just one failed handbrake turn away from federal investigation and becoming a legend of the San Andreas racing circuit. Lap race for Los Santos Tuners.

name: Street Race - Country Pursuits
desc: Everyone dreams of leaving their small town for the big city. But you? You bring the big city to the small town, including the all-out precision racing, traffic law violations and horrifying injuries. Better hope The Bay Care Center is well equipped. Lap race for Los Santos Tuners.
creator: RSI_sidhant

name: Street Race - Home Street Home
creator: RSI_sidhant
desc: You know the score: You grew up on the streets of Strawberry. You race on the streets of Strawberry. And one day they'll scrape you off the streets of Strawberry. Get ready for your whole life to flash before your eyes. Lap race for Los Santos Tuners.

name: Street Race - Beachfront Runner
desc: You know how to party in Del Perro. Beat LS's legendary drivers in a breakneck street race, slam some cocktails at Bahama Mamas, blackout on the dancefloor, and wake up spewing cotton candy on Pleasure Pier. Time to initiate phase one. Lap race for Los Santos Tuners.
creator: RSGIND_CastroA

name: Street Race - Back at the Rancho
creator: RSGIND_CastroA
desc: This high-octane street race is the most exciting cultural event to hit Rancho since the reshoot of Die Already 4. Although, the body count is expected to be just as high. Lap race for Los Santos Tuners.

name: Street Race - High Society
desc: The community council of Rockford Hills have issued a formal complaint over the reckless racing in their good, god-fearing American streets. There's only one rational response. Settle into the power-slide, pull down your pants, and drop a fat deuce out of the window as you pass the AGM. Lap race for Los Santos Tuners.
creator: RSI_sidhant

name: Street Race - Up Your Alley
creator: RSGIND_CastroA
desc: Careering down the alleyways of Mission Row, you'll always find one of three things. 1) A mugging. 2) A handjob. 3) A street race shortcut. Fingers crossed for number three and/or number two. Lap race for Los Santos Tuners.
